<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Ikura Donburi | Taste The Movies</title>
</head>
<body>

  <header>
    <h1>Taste The Movies</h1>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section>
      <div>
        <img src="images/placeholder.png" alt="Salmon Roe Rice Bowl from Ponyo" />
      </div>
      <div>
        <h2>Salmon Roe Rice Bowl with Egg and Green Onion</h2>
        <p><strong>Description:</strong></p>
        <p>This comforting and simple dish, inspired by the movie *Ponyo*, combines the delicate flavors of salmon roe, scrambled egg, and fresh green onions atop warm rice.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section>
      <div>
        <h3>Ingredients</h3>
        <ul>
          <li>Cooked white rice</li>
          <li>1 egg, lightly scrambled</li>
          <li>2 tbsp salmon roe (ikura)</li>
          <li>Green onion</li>
          <li>Soy sauce</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h3>Instructions</h3>
        <ol>
          <li>Place hot rice in a bowl.</li>
          <li>Top with scrambled egg, salmon roe, and green onions.</li>
          <li>Drizzle with soy sauce to taste.</li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer>
  </footer>

</body>
</html>

